Comment: 0,0:23:39.94,0:23:39.97,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Prévia} = Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.37,0:23:42.96,Default - Italics,,0,0,0,,Foi a Besta quem matou a Riko.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.34,0:23:44.68,Default - Italics,,0,0,0,,Ela terá o que merece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.68,0:23:48.34,Default - Italics,,0,0,0,,Himeya, não adianta tentar salvar o Komon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.88,0:23:51.15,Default - Italics,,0,0,0,,Mizorogi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.46,0:23:55.72,Default - Italics,,0,0,0,,Fique quieto e assista-o ser consumido pelas trevas.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.70,0:24:06.96,Default - Top Italics,,0,0,0,,Komon!
